txt.en:
This item will complete certain quests available in Rohan, granting the Class Trait Points they come with.

<rgb=#ff0000>If you use this item, this character can never play the following quests and deeds.</rgb>

This completes the quests and deeds:

'The Road to Dunharrow'
'All Roads Lead Back to Aldburg'
'To Helm's Deep'
'Promotion Points 1'
'Promotion Points 2'
